  <brief_title>The Effect of Reduced Dose of Enoxaparin on the Outcomes of Treatment With Enoxaparin</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Reduced Dose of Enoxaparin on the Laboratory and Clinical Outcomes of Treatment With Enoxaparin</official_title>
